---
# Benchmarks use the Google Benchmark `for (auto _ : state)` loop, which the
# dead-store analyzer flags, and seed their RNGs with fixed constants so a run
# is reproducible. Both are intentional in a microbenchmark, so disable the
# matching checks here while inheriting the rest of the project policy.
InheritParentConfig: true
Checks: >
  -clang-analyzer-deadcode.DeadStores,
  -cert-msc32-c,
  -cert-msc51-cpp
